        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "雪国特有の雁木の下を歩けば、吹雪の日でも傘をささずに買い物を楽しむことができる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「船が着くから、雁木の階段まで荷物を運ぶのを手伝ってくれないか？」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "釣り人たちは雁木に腰掛け、のんびりと糸を垂らしながら世間話に花を咲かせていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "pathway covered by extended eaves to protect from snow",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "雪深い京都の古い町屋では、冬になると雁木がお家を守ってくれるんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "雁木を歩いていると、しんしんと降る雪の音だけが聞こえてきたよ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "昔の宿場町では、雨や雪を避けるために雁木が発達していたらしい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "large saw used by lumberjacks",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "昔の木こりたちは、太い木を倒すためにあの大きな雁木を使っていたんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "現場には、うわさの巨大な雁木が立てかけられていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "あの丸太を製材するには、相当な腕と頑丈な雁木が必要だろうな。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
